003/**
004 * Classe Command - une commande du jeu d'aventure Zuul.
005 *
006 * @author votre nom
007 */
008public class Command
009{
010    private String aCommandWord;
011    private String aSecondWord;
012    
013    public Command(final String pCommandWord, final String pSecondWord) {
014        this.aCommandWord = pCommandWord;
015        this.aSecondWord = pSecondWord;
016    } // Command()
017    
018    public String getCommandWord() {
019        return this.aCommandWord;
020    } // getCommandWord()
021    
022    public String getSecondWord() {
023        return this.aSecondWord;
024    } // getSecondWord()
025    
026    public boolean hasSecondWord() {
027        return this.aSecondWord != null;
028    }
029    
030    public boolean isUnknown() {
031        return this.aCommandWord == null;
032    }
033} // Command
